                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-116" type="given" value="JOSEPH HENRY"></interp>JOSEPH HENRY TAYLOR</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, T</hi> 115.) I was called to Mr. East's, on 31st March—I took the prisoner, and found 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in his left waistcoat pocket; 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. of it was marked.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
